data.description: The Hawthorn plan provides a flex room with double French doors and a nearby half bath on the main level along with an open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, Quartz countertops, and a breakfast bar island, overlooking a comfortable great room and a  dining area.  Off the dining area, the center-meet sliding doors provide access to a covered patio. The upstairs offers a versatile loft and two more bedrooms and  a spacious owner's suite boasting a roomy walk-in closet and attached bath.
